00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:31.419
- [Narrator] We are the paradoxical ape:
bipedal, naked, large-brained. Long the

00:00:31.419 --> 00:00:37.804
master of fire, tools and language, but
still trying to understand ourselves.

00:00:37.804 --> 00:00:48.579
Aware that death is inevitable yet filled
with optimism. We grow up slowly. We

00:00:48.579 --> 00:00:55.777
hand down knowledge, we empathize and
deceive. We shape the future from our

00:00:55.777 --> 00:01:02.776
shared understanding of the past. CARTA
brings together experts from diverse

00:01:02.776 --> 00:01:10.578
disciplines to exchange insights on who we
are and how we got here, an exploration

00:01:10.578 --> 00:01:14.827
made possible by the generosity of
humans like you.

00:01:30.485 --> 00:01:33.485
